    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当神秘的星之碎片与地球的生命产生共鸣，化作一颗颗充满力量的骰子——世界因此改变。三颗骰子一同掷出，不仅能决定你的行动，更将释放意想不到的能量。真相或许无人知晓，但也无需深究。重要的是，选择与你心灵相通的宠物伙伴，组成三人小队，在热闹的派对中掷出你的命运，成为最终的赢家！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >骰子，不只是运气</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >灵感源自经典游戏“骰宝”，每位角色都拥有专属的押注组合。每次投掷不仅用于移动，还可能为你带来额外奖励。如果结果不尽人意，你甚至可以亲手“调整”骰面点数——是机智操作，还是暗中捣鬼？由你定义。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/04ac6f329485a44ec1e20d9c36cb68dc.poster.avif?t=1767923167\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/04ac6f329485a44ec1e20d9c36cb68dc.webm?t=1767923167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/04ac6f329485a44ec1e20d9c36cb68dc.mp4?t=1767923167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快节奏同步乱斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持最多 8 人同局，所有玩家同步行动——无需等待，永远是你的回合！瞬间的决策、即时的反馈，让战局瞬息万变，欢乐与刺激从不间断。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/f7c912734bae9f7420c3442e69ca7d5d.poster.avif?t=1767923167\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/f7c912734bae9f7420c3442e69ca7d5d.webm?t=1767923167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/f7c912734bae9f7420c3442e69ca7d5d.mp4?t=1767923167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >策略由你，正邪自选</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以稳健运营：收集星星、经营地盘、探寻宝藏、通过猜拳决斗战胜对手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也可以化身“捣蛋鬼”：偷窃、抢劫、栽赃、陷害……只要能获得更多星星，一切手段皆合理。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/46ec13c9fe18ec368bc74e4e7491b0a5.poster.avif?t=1767923167\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/46ec13c9fe18ec368bc74e4e7491b0a5.webm?t=1767923167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/46ec13c9fe18ec368bc74e4e7491b0a5.mp4?t=1767923167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深度构筑，千变万化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ 风格迥异的角色，25+ 可招募的宠物伙伴，160+ 张效果各异的卡牌，50+ 种强力宝物。自由搭配角色、伙伴、卡牌与宝物，构建属于你自己的战斗风格。每一局都是全新的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/5ff650519c2fa3a20b9616f13da12fb1.poster.avif?t=1767923167\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/5ff650519c2fa3a20b9616f13da12fb1.webm?t=1767923167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065140/extras/5ff650519c2fa3a20b9616f13da12fb1.mp4?t=1767923167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >漫游全球，沉浸式都市探险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们精心选取世界知名城市，以精致卡通风格还原其标志性建筑与独特街景。每张地图不仅布局各异，更融入了对应的文化氛围与互动元素，让你在畅快游戏的同时，感受不同城市的独特氛围。</p>",
